---

<Layout title="feifan.dev">
  <header class="hero glass-panel">
    <span class="chip">Senior full-stack engineer</span>
    <h1>Feifan builds resilient platforms for high-scale product and operations teams.</h1>
    <p>
      Senior Full-Stack Developer at Flight Centre building scalable booking, document, and communication
      platforms, with hands-on experience across banking systems, energy tooling, and cloud-native delivery.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-links">
      <a class="hero-cta" href="#experience">Browse recent work</a>
      <a class="hero-secondary" href="/thoughts">Read field notes</a>
      <a class="hero-secondary" href="mailto:hi@feifan.dev?subject=Project%20chat">Book a call</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
      Hi, I’m Feifan—a Brisbane-based software engineer currently working at Flight Centre,
      where I contribute to production-grade platforms and mentor developers across the team.
      I’ve previously modernized energy systems at Edge2020, delivered learning platforms at JR Academy,
      and built high-availability transaction services in banking.
    </p>
    <p>
      My focus is practical, maintainable software: event-driven architecture, reliable delivery pipelines,
      and clean developer workflows including AI-assisted engineering. Longer essays and lab notes live on
      <a href="/thoughts">the Thoughts page</a> if you’d like the details.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="experience">
    <h2>Experience</h2>
    <ExperienceTimeline items={experience} />
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .hero-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-cta,
  .hero-secondary {
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .hero-cta:hover,
  .hero-cta:focus-visible,
  .hero-secondary:hover,
  .hero-secondary:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 2.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
